biểu tại 3D Smart Solutions:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/Pr8153A4.png">Link</a><br>[3DS] C&aacute;c giải ph&aacute;p v&agrave; dự &aacute;n ti&ecirc;u biểu:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/kPw8Zp1Y.png">Link</a><br><br><strong>3. Ứng dụng</strong><br><a href="http://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/tap-tin/35604b41a598455d7c5d5a043791f8ec9f3115128dc846e6c293ec97d0d8b5bf/download" target="_blank" style="mso-line-height-rule: exactly; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; color: #007c89; font-weight: normal; text-decoration: underline;" rel="noopener"></a>Ứng dụng in 3D trong đ&agrave;o tạo y tế:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/qgH2ivvL.png">Link</a><br>Ứng dụng c&ocirc;ng nghệ 3D trong sản xuất tay ch&acirc;n giả:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/A4lkW0mU.png">Link</a><br>Ứng dụng in 3D trong sản xuất đạo cụ h&oacute;a trang:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/Uw6hcQI1.png">Link</a><br><br><strong>4. Sản phẩm</strong><br><a href="http://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/tap-tin/4fe66c595717b9e8f1b7d814bf5c4dfa713d1975cd7ed6e8bef6b7a99d265722/download" target="_blank" style="mso-line-height-rule: exactly; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; color: #007c89; font-weight: normal; text-decoration: underline;" rel="noopener"></a>[Sản phẩm] M&aacute;y qu&eacute;t 3D cầm tay EinStar:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/hBAwQcUh.png">Link</a><br>Sản phẩm mới Formlabs V2:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/2Mh6kIuJ.png">Link</a><br><br><strong>5. Kh&aacute;m ph&aacute;<br></strong>[Kh&aacute;m ph&aacute;] Nhựa Nylon ứng dụng trong in 3D:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/H1LYew4p.png">Link</a><br>Kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; ch&uacute; khủng long khổng lồ từ c&ocirc;ng nghệ 3D:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/bj0icif0.png">Link</a><br>Kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; lợi thế tuyệt vời của nhựa PLA trong in 3D:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/Wf4swVgB.png">Link</a><br>Kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; về vật liệu nhựa TPU in 3D:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/V6UD4JEd.png">Link</a><br>In 3D khu&ocirc;n &eacute;p nhựa bằng resin Rigid 10K:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/f5WBVo1M.png">Link</a><br>Tổng hợp c&aacute;c lỗi m&aacute;y in 3D v&agrave; c&aacute;ch khắc phục:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/zPlxtQsd.png">Link</a><br>[3DS] GIỚI THIỆU M&Aacute;Y IN 3D METAL PRINTER - EOS M290:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/Rg2IOxtq.png">Link</a><br>T&igrave;m hiểu về c&ocirc;ng nghệ in nhựa 3D:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/jwVJUe3X.png">Link</a><br>10 t&iacute;nh năng của Mastercam 2023 bạn cần biết:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/xXdVxQfA.png">Link</a><br>C&ocirc;ng nghệ in 3D m&agrave;u v&agrave; những lưu &yacute; cần biết:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/s5caXqsV.png">Link</a><br>Thiết kế in 3D v&agrave; c&aacute;c ti&ecirc;u ch&iacute; đ&aacute;nh gi&aacute; một thiết kế in 3D ph&ugrave; hợp:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/ryvD95ug.png">Link</a><br><br><strong>6. Chuyển giao c&ocirc;ng nghệ<br></strong>Chuyển giao c&ocirc;ng nghệ in 3D - Formlabs Form 3L tại Schaeffler:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/dmg4vlQW.png">Link</a><br>Chuyển giao Bộ giải ph&aacute;p - C&ocirc;ng nghệ 3D cho FABTEK Việt Nam:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/m3org1QF.png">Link</a><br><br><strong>7. Li&ecirc;n quan đến đơn h&agrave;ng,hợp đồng &amp; b&aacute;o gi&aacute;</strong><br>[3DS] Nhắc hẹn thanh to&aacute;n:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/V9b8eZg9.png">Link</a><br>[3DS] X&aacute;c nhận thanh to&aacute;n:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/Fv0eGiCs.png">Link</a><br>[3DS] Thư cảm ơn:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/CP4BFFTt.png">Link</a><br>[3DS] B&aacute;o gi&aacute; dịch vụ Tạo mẫu nhanh (3D Print):&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/5ZZFDo8D.png">Link</a><br>[3DS] B&aacute;o gi&aacute; dịch vụ Qu&eacute;t mẫu 3D (Scan Only):&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/bQHJNpO5.png">Link</a><br>[3DS] B&aacute;o gi&aacute; dịch vụ Thiết kế ngược (Reverse Engineering):&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/SfNCW2gf.png">Link</a><br>[3DS] B&aacute;o gi&aacute; dịch vụ Kiểm tra k&iacute;ch thước (Inspection):&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/tEaDSDYI.png">Link</a><br>[3DS] Th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o về hợp đồng:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/dEqXccsc.png">Link</a><br><br><strong>8. Th&ocirc;ng tin kh&aacute;c</strong><br>Lời nhắn từ CEO [B2B]:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/8XB0UtRO.png">Link</a><br>[3Dm] Lời Ch&agrave;o Từ Founder 3Dmanufacturer:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/x70XT2K3.png">Link</a><br>[3DS] Thư ngỏ (team BD):&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.3d-smartsolutions.com/shared/users/103/folders-3275/kic4PLqC.png">Link</a><br>[